InfoItems.Info: Converted GDTF to grandMA2 fixture type with Share Converter version 1.4.1
New fixture type based on Robin T3 Fresnel from Robe Lighting

T3 Fresnel Building on the acclaimed success and exceptional quality of the highly acclaimed Robe T-Series, the T3 FresnelTM elevates highpower multispectral wash performance to the ultimate level. Designed for Long-Throw wash applications in the world’s largest theatres, opera houses and concert halls, it delivers unparalleled output, light quality and precise colour control. Delivering over 35.000 lumens (integrating sphere) from its powerful 1.400W MSLTM (Multi-Spectral-Light) source, the T3 FresnelTM stays true to its theatrical heritage with its classically soft Fresnel style beam ensuring the smoothest wash coverage across the largest theatres and studios with its wide ranging 6 - 65° zoom.
